snippet.title: Fairune Collection - Nintendo Switch teaser!
snippet.description:
Take a look at Fairune Collection in this special Nintendo Switch teaser. Out on 17th May on the Switch eShop and Steam, eShop pre-orders open on 10th May with a 10% discount!

Follow us on Twitter for more updates - https://twitter.com/FlyhighWorks_en
